<td><a href="/wiki/Kidnapping" title="Kidnapping">Kidnapping</a>, <a href="/wiki/Rape" title="Rape">rape</a>,<sup id="cite_ref-plain-dealer-charges_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-plain-dealer-charges-1">[1]</a></sup> aggravated <a href="/wiki/Murder" title="Murder">murder</a>, <a href="/wiki/Attempted_murder" title="Attempted murder">attempted murder</a>, <a href="/wiki/Assault" title="Assault">assault</a><sup id="cite_ref-pd090513_2-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-pd090513-2">[2]</a></sup></td>
