<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Films">Films</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Ariel_Castro_kidnappings&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Films">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><cite class="citation audio-visual"><i><a href="/wiki/Cleveland_Abduction" title="Cleveland Abduction">Cleveland Abduction</a></i> (<a href="/wiki/Television_film" title="Television film">Television film</a>). <a href="/wiki/Lifetime_(TV_network)" title="Lifetime (TV network)">Lifetime</a>. 2015.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAriel+Castro+kidnappings&amp;rft.btitle=Cleveland+Abduction&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.pub=Lifetime&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span><sup id="cite_ref-132" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-132">[132]</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-133" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-133">[133]</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-134" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-134">[134]</a></sup></li>
